item.title: About me
item.description: Hi, my name is David and I am a programmer. I studied computer science at Umass Amherst and now I write code for my job and in my free time for fun. I always hear people say “Teaching is the best way to learn.” So that is what I intend to do here. With each post I will try to explain a subject to better my own understanding of it and hopefully teach you something along the way.
